-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
USER INTERFACE:
Stuff about the interface with the user
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
The Software shall include a graphical user interface (GUI)
The GUI shall have the capability to add a new client to the database 
The GUI shall have the capability to edit the information of an existing client in the database 
The GUI shall have the capability to add a new user to the database 
The GUI shall have the capability to edit the information of an existing user in the database 
The GUI shall have the capability to add a new hardware to the database 
The GUI shall have the capability to edit the information of an existing hardware in the database
The GUI shall allow the creation/edition/deletion of services (see services category for more details)
The GUI shall have include the service option to send an email with information about the diagnostic of device and cost of repair (service status) to the client
The GUI shall have include the option to send a print of the service report
The GUI shall have include the service option to show the progress of each service
The GUI shall have include the dashboard option to show the pending tasks
The GUI shall have include the dashboard option to show who is checking each device
The GUI shall have include the dashboard option to show the devices status 
The GUI shall be designed for touchscreen usage as much as possible (drag items, drop them, etc)

-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
HARDWARE:
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
The hardware shall have the model of device
The hardware shall have the brand of device
The hardware shall have the type of device
The hardware shall have the physical description of the device
The hardware shall have the serial number of the device

